Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title}Hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink too much even if your customer asks you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always the one picking you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I have such a capable sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where Judy Devens passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone called you Phantom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from Judy's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that kills people in American gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a true assassin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an assassin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assassin, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys who were at the alley last night, the guys who shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the guys who were supposed to retrieve the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill all the people who caused Judy's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji will definitely avenge you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that five million...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only need a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could make it even by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my assistant in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so if I become your assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to see the moment when Judy gets avenged with my own eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, there's something you need to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick the one you want the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want all the clothes here equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just picked one, I'd have to give up the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the only chance that you'll get to shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you here again if there's something else you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so pick a set of clothes you want to wear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, is it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks really good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time wearing such light clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook after I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's really dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An assassin who cleans his own house doesn't sound too tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave something like this to your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to earn that money on top of the five million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Reiji, do you have any family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your parents already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away from my bastard old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then Judy took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she hadn't, I'd be dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, she's my only family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Judy died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to do now that Judy's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like you once,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not knowing what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many ways to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reward for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat it with a lot of care...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the actors have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, the woman who used me through crafty tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now wants to create another scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godoh Daisuke, her partner who wants to make inroads into Inferno along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisemel, the one who discovered the conspiracy and is trying to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's another new actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me create the best stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time to get busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that sniper be Judy's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, they're part of the same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me witness it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Someone's there behind the water tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me that face of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.90,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Mr. Godoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get shot? Did you hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it just scratched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to see that person's face no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who killed Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've avenged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Withdraw via route C immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard some rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Issac of the Bloodies died?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then avenging Judy is done...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my assassin training?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's fine with you, I can help you with your assassinations from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to miss your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll let you be my kitchen maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yay! Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid clothes are really cute, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to become your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you don't want me to become an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you know the pain of an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, you can walk whatever path you want. Do whatever you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you want to become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you hate yourself too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing is like my second nature and I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to become like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Reiji... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many have died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't there, they would still be living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could have all gone back to their families and lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just accepted a job that was going to be done either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as pretty as you described...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you really want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you shoot just because you want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you kill your first person, the whole world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you see... Everything you hear... Everything changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be your kind self anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't come into the world that I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll always stay in there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go there, then I'll always be able to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really do want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need. I'll go to your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go... Let me go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the world where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji said he'll stay by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you've got work this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up a broken video cassette recorder during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it can still be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can still be used, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I think the video store is still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji! Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiji is... Reiji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wouldn't leave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd be with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. He's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been deceived this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can be like your old self...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
